---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Terms of Service — AIdeaPulse" description="Terms governing your use of the AIdeaPulse platform.">
  <div class="space-y-8">
    <div>
      <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-400 mt-2 text-sm">Last updated: March 28, 2026</p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-8 text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        These Terms of Service ("Terms") govern your access to and use of the AIdeaPulse website at aideapulse.com and all related services (collectively, the "Service") operated by AIdeaPulse ("we," "us," or "our"). By accessing or using the Service, you agree to be bound by these Terms. If you do not agree, do not use the Service.
      </p>

      <!-- Section 1 -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">1. Description of Service</h2>
        <p>AIdeaPulse is an AI-powered startup idea discovery platform. The Service aggregates publicly available data from third-party sources, analyzes it using artificial intelligence, and presents structured startup idea briefs to users. The Service is provided on a subscription basis with a free tier and a paid tier.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Section 2 -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">2. Eligibility</h2>
        <p>You must be at least 16 years of age to use the Service.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Section 3 -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">3. Account Registration</h2>
        <p>To access certain features, you must create an account through Clerk. You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your account credentials. We reserve the right to suspend or terminate accounts that violate these Terms.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Section 4 -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">4. Subscription Plans and Pricing</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-cyan-400 mt-1">•</span>
            <span><strong class="text-white">Free Tier:</strong> Access to up to 50 idea previews per day, one full idea unlock per day (daily free claim), basic idea information (title, source, confidence score, complexity).</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-cyan-400 mt-1">•</span>
            <span><strong class="text-white">Pro Tier ($12/month):</strong> Access to up to 1,000 ideas per day, full idea details including problem statements, target audiences, market sizing, competitor analysis, build timelines, and monetization angles, email digest notifications, saved ideas functionality.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-3">Pricing is subject to change with at least 30 days notice for existing subscribers.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Section 5 -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">5. Payments and Billing</h2>
        <p>Pro subscriptions are billed monthly through Stripe. Subscriptions renew automatically. You may cancel at any time — cancellation takes effect at the end of the current billing period. We do not provide refunds for partial billing periods. Contact support@aideapulse.com within 14 days if charged in error.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Section 6 -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">6. Acceptable Use</h2>
        <p class="mb-3">You agree not to:</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-cyan-400 mt-1">•</span><span>Use the Service unlawfully</span></li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-cyan-400 mt-1">•</span><span>Attempt unauthorized access</span></li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-cyan-400 mt-1">•</span><span>Use bots or scrapers</span></li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-cyan-400 mt-1">•</span><span>Circumvent rate limits or security features</span></li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-cyan-400 mt-1">•</span><span>Reverse engineer the Service</span></li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-cyan-400 mt-1">•</span><span>Resell or redistribute content</span></li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-cyan-400 mt-1">•</span><span>Build a competing product</span></li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-cyan-400 mt-1">•</span><span>Misrepresent your identity</span></li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-cyan-400 mt-1">•</span><span>Interfere with service performance</span></li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-3">We may suspend or terminate access for violations.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Section 7 -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">7. Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p class="mb-3"><strong class="text-white">Our Content:</strong> The Service design, code, features, and branding are owned by AIdeaPulse.</p>
        <p class="mb-3"><strong class="text-white">Idea Briefs:</strong> We do not claim exclusive ownership over underlying business concepts. The specific presentation, analysis, scoring, and formatting are our proprietary content. You may use idea briefs for personal or business evaluation. You may not systematically reproduce or redistribute them in bulk.</p>
        <p><strong class="text-white">Your Content:</strong> Content you submit remains yours. You grant us a limited license to use it to operate and improve the Service.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Section 8 -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">8. AI-Generated Content Disclaimer</h2>
        <p>All idea briefs, scores, and analyses are produced by AI and provided for informational and exploratory purposes only. We make no warranties regarding accuracy, completeness, viability, or suitability. AI-generated content does not constitute business, financial, investment, or legal advice. You are solely responsible for your own due diligence.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Section 9 -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">9. Third-Party Services and Data Sources</h2>
        <p>The Service aggregates data from Reddit, Hacker News, Product Hunt, GitHub, Dev.to, Lobsters, NewsAPI, and Google Trends. We are not affiliated with these platforms. The Service integrates with Clerk, Stripe, Cloudflare, and Resend — your use of those services is subject to their respective terms.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Section 10 -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">10. Service Availability</h2>
        <p>We do not guarantee uninterrupted or error-free operation. We may modify, suspend, or discontinue any part of the Service at any time.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Section 11 -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">11. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>The Service is provided "as is" and "as available" without warranties. We shall not be liable for indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages. Our total aggregate liability shall not exceed the amount you paid us in the twelve months preceding the claim.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Section 12 -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">12. Indemnification</h2>
        <p>You agree to indemnify and hold harmless AIdeaPulse and its owner from claims arising from your use of the Service or violation of these Terms.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Section 13 -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">13. Termination</h2>
        <p>We may suspend or terminate access at any time. Upon termination, your access ceases, subscriptions will not renew, and we may delete your data per the Privacy Policy. Sections 7, 8, 11, 12, and 14 survive termination.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Section 14 -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">14. Governing Law</h2>
        <p>These Terms are governed by the laws of the State of Texas. Disputes shall be resolved in state or federal courts located in Texas.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Section 15 -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">15. Changes to These Terms</h2>
        <p>We may update these Terms. Material changes to pricing or scope will have at least 30 days advance notice.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Section 16 -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">16. Severability</h2>
        <p>If any provision is unenforceable, the remaining provisions remain in effect.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Section 17 -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">17. Entire Agreement</h2>
        <p>These Terms and our <a href="/privacy" class="text-cyan-400 hover:underline">Privacy Policy</a> constitute the entire agreement.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Section 18 -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">18. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>Email: support@aideapulse.com</p>
        <p>Website: <a href="https://aideapulse.com" class="text-cyan-400 hover:underline">aideapulse.com</a></p>
      </div>

      <!-- Cross-link -->
      <div class="pt-4 border-t border-gray-800">
        <p class="text-sm">See also our <a href="/privacy" class="text-cyan-400 hover:underline">Privacy Policy</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="pt-4 border-t border-gray-800">
      <a href="/" class="text-cyan-400 hover:underline text-sm">
        &larr; Browse ideas
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
